{"000-section": {"000-title": "Haryana Parivar Pehchan Patra (Identity Certificate) for Every Family to Curb Corruption"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "Haryana govt. to make Parivar Pehchan Patra for approx. 54 lakh families (46 lakh in SECC 2011 data plus 8 lakh others), family identity certificate application form performa to remain available at SDM offices, tehsil & block offices, schools, ration depot, gas agencies & other public dealing offices"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Haryana Parivar Pehchan Patra (Family Identity Certificate)", "001-normal": "After the updation of data of family on the basis of residence, death and birth, the state government is consistently working to update data of families on the basis of [SECC-2011 data](https://sarkariyojana.com/all-india-bpl-list-2018-download-secc-2011-data/). Till date, there are around 54 lakh families in the state which would get included in the updated database. To apply for Parivar Pehchan Patra in Haryana, all the people needs to fill the application form and submit it to the concerned authorities.", "002-normal": "CM has instructed all the officials to keep a performa of Family Identity Certificate in their offices. The application forms for Parivar Pehchan Patra will remain available at all the SDM offices, tehsil & block offices, schools, ration depot, gas agencies and other offices which deals with the general public.", "003-normal": "This availability of Haryana Parivar Pehchan Patra application forms at public dealing offices would ensure that people who comes to these offices to take benefits of government schemes can update their family details. Moreover, the state govt. is also working to simplify the process of making of birth certificate, death certificate and marriage registration certificate.", "004-normal": "\u0905\u092c \u0939\u0930 \u092a\u0930\u093f\u0935\u093e\u0930 \u0915\u093e \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e \u092a\u0939\u091a\u093e\u0928 \u092a\u0924\u094d\u0930; \u092d\u094d\u0930\u0937\u094d\u091f\u093e\u091a\u093e\u0930 \u092a\u0930 \u0932\u0917\u0947\u0917\u093e \u0905\u0902\u0915\u0941\u0936\u0964 [pic.twitter.com/AdmUeawY5W](https://t.co/AdmUeawY5W)", "005-normal": "\u2014 CMO Haryana (@cmohry) [January 2, 2019](https://twitter.com/cmohry/status/1080367236286767104?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)", "006-normal": "", "007-normal": "The data would be used by the departments to give benefit of various welfare services to its actual beneficiary. This family identity certificate would also remove duplication as Aadhaar number and phone number of the beneficiary would also be updated in the \u2018Parivar Pehchan Patra\u2019 performa.", "008-normal": "The information regarding various govt. schemes must reach the people. For instance, if a person reaches the age of 60 years, then he / she must information that they now becomes eligible for [Old Age Pension Scheme in Haryana](https://sarkariyojana.com/haryana-old-age-pension-scheme-2018-registration-status-beneficiary-list/). Similarly if any youth attains the age of 18 years, then he / she must get information about he / she is eligible for voting."}}